Customer Feedback:

{quote}
1st off as this is the first time contacting you - the windows version of source tree thus far seems great. I've never had such as easy installation process to get GIT working... good job!

Onto my issue, the "Working Copy Changes" seems a little slow at times (I believe this is due to preview content trying to load?). It has caused me to double click items accidentely (opening the files) and struggling to get the selection I wanted with as much ease as I expected. Fairly minor but a little annoying for a pane I imagine is used a lot.

My version is 0.8.2.0 (isn't listed in the versions dropdown on your site).
{quote}
